# This file fixed default WebKit style settings by command:
#     clang-format -style=WebKit -dump-config > .clang-format
# You must install clang-format before use it. If you do not want be format
#
# please add follow two comment
#     // clang-format off  or  /* clang-format off */
#     NOT WANT BE FORMATE  CODE
#     // clang-format on or  /* clang-format on */
# More information please check clang-format(maybe clang-format-3.9) --help
#
# History:
#     2017/07/15, wiki first release;
#     2018/02/02, update
#
# Reference
#     http://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormatStyleOptions.html
#     http://www.cnblogs.com/PaulpauL/p/5929753.html

